metadata.name: Boss Dimension c-96
metadata.description:
In a dimension far, far away the C-96 dimension was being watched by the Big Boss, but one day intruder Pepe Sanchez and his beloved grandchildren trespassed on Big Boss’ galaxy, and this was not welcomed. They got into trouble on their adventure. They realized when it was all too late that the portal gun was running out of fuel. Now is the time to run and hide!  Do you think this adventurous team will be able to escape, chased by the pop culture tribe at the command of the big boss?
